data.description: Located in a very desirable and quite area, just a few minutes from I-10, the outlet malls, grocery and more.  The homes is a very popular DR Horton floorplan featuring 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, plus a den/office area.  10 Ft. ceilings, granite countertops, SS appliances and HUGE laundry room, pantry and 3 car garage make this one especially desirable.  Low HOA fee's for this beautiful subdivision that features a great park, as well. Truly a must see!!!
